articles.title: BABYMONSTER's highly anticipated debut 'Batter Up' is a swing and a miss - NME
articles.description: BABYMONSTER, the first girl group to debut under YG Ent. since BLACKPINK, contend with lazy songwriting and a tired formula on 'Batter Up'
articles.content: Attention! goes the cry at the start of Batter Up, the debut single from YG Entertainments new girl group, BABYMONSTER. Its a fitting way to kick off their story a call to order after months of rumou… [+3225 chars]
